data.description: Price Improvement!!!!  Welcome to the highly sought-after neighborhood of Woodshore! This home offers the perfect blend of comfort and character.  This exceptional two story floorplan boasts with a 4 BR, 2.5 BA, downstairs primary and study, walk in closets, high ceilings, an upstairs game room and media room!  Enjoy the seamless transitions from tile, vinyl plank, and carpet flooring as you're greeted by each effortless entertainment or relaxing space.
